{"tid":625024,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[理大煙民] 啱啱係poly見到有三條友食煙，影左相再走去問候佢地（全家）","createTime":"2018-04-11T06:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T11:19:00.000Z","uid":127929,"like":1549,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"0a4661e62da94068acb6e294f8f9906bd364f488","tid":625024,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:05:19.000Z","msg":"地點: polyu QR core 樓梯6 樓<br />\n日期: 11-4-2018，中午1點左右<br />\n<br />\n本來諗住落樓去七仔買野，行到6 樓樓梯附近聞到好大陣煙味，結果行埋去見到三條操大陸口音既人係度打邊爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/133315_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F133315_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=a2215978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我個下直行直過，但落到5樓仲好似比人煙燻咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頂唔順之下我決定行返上去，一邊扮打電話一邊拍片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後其中有條友係正我面前拎起支煙，我火起上黎就開始問候佢地:<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大陸仔:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :喂你地三個係咩事架係度?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :（即刻收起支煙）只是聊聊而已呵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :你地知唔知道大學唔比食煙?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : ...（好似聽唔明我up乜）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :（我指去隔離不准吸煙個logo）你地食咩煙呀係度?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : ...那個... 沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咱都不會抽這個東西（然後有其他人入左黎樓梯，佢三個偷雞光速閃人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/140019_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F140019_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7a951ac1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/140036_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F140036_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3b1a70f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有冇人知佢地係咩department, 想去report佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"82890968b20969a89d27b296fa1d8c8b48ba2cf9","tid":625024,"uid":127929,"like":404,"dislike":7,"score":397,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:07:36.000Z","msg":"要食煙就死返支那啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98604947973c2c5c27958ef3c982159d0fc7de37","tid":625024,"uid":29620,"like":62,"dislike":2,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:08:12.000Z","msg":"有片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3333188efbd8263d052e7b3063d6769e660508e","tid":625024,"uid":135445,"like":99,"dislike":2,"score":97,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:09:13.000Z","msg":"巴打好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f9bdf28d607eb50537720997bb688b7267b77ec","tid":625024,"uid":158317,"like":82,"dislike":2,"score":80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:13:47.000Z","msg":"巴打勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855b99312669d41013f61e4e2f8c93650116c02e","tid":625024,"uid":41292,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:16:35.000Z","msg":"Report<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327383a01c